OL,3,CMan accused of sending MLA threatening
OL,4,Cmessages
OL,6,FA man has appeared before court
OL,7,Faccused of sending threatening
OL,8,Fmessages to DUP MLA Trevor Clarke.
OL,10,FAndrew Moran, 30, of Grange Lane,
OL,11,FNewtownabbey, faces seven charges in
OL,12,Ftotal.
OL,14,FThey include sending threatening
OL,15,Felectronic messages, possession of
OL,16,Fcannabis and breaching a restraining
OL,17,Forder.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
