PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1775160364
OL,3,CMan accused of sending MLA threatening
OL,4,Cmessages
OL,6,FThere is also a charge for
OL,7,Fintimidation of a witness on March 29
OL,8,F2026 for allegedly threatening Mr
OL,9,FClarke for speaking with police, and
OL,10,Ffor allegedly harassing Mr Clarke
OL,11,Fbetween March 27 and April 1.
OL,13,FFollowing a brief mention at Ballymena
OL,14,FMagistrates' Court on Thursday
OL,15,Fmorning, Moran was remanded into
OL,16,Fcustody after the case was adjourned
OL,17,Fon request of the defence because it
OL,18,Fwas not ready.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/3
